OL,7,FHe told me he feels "vindicated" by
OL,8,Fthe judge's ruling that senior figures
OL,9,Fat the newspaper group knew about
OL,10,Funlawful activities.
OL,12,F"To have the judge rule in our favour
OL,13,Fwas obviously huge. But for him to go
OL,14,Fas far as he did... this wasn't just
