OL,4,C'vindicated' Prince Harry on impact of
OL,5,Chacking
OL,7,FIn December 2023, a judge ruled that
OL,8,FPrince Harry's voicemails had been
OL,9,Fintercepted and his private
OL,10,Finformation unlawfully obtained by the
OL,11,FDaily Mirror, Sunday Mirror and The
OL,12,FPeople.
OL,14,FPrince Harry says he feels
OL,15,F"vindicated" by the judge's ruling in
OL,16,Fthe phone hacking case last year
OL,18,FPrince Harry told me it had caused him
OL,19,F"paranoia, fear and distrust".
