OL,7,FA judge ruled 15 out of 33 Mirror
OL,8,FGroup Newspapers articles - including
OL,9,Fstories about his past girlfriends, a
OL,10,Fconversation with his brother, his
OL,11,Fdeployments to Afghanistan - were all
OL,12,Fthe result of phone hacking, so-called
OL,13,F"blagging" or other unlawful
OL,14,Factivities.
OL,16,F"When you're vindicated," Prince Harry
OL,17,Ftold me, "it proves that you weren't
OL,18,Fbeing paranoid".
