OL,7,FHe's since discovered he was hacked by
OL,8,Fthe News of the World. In 2011, News
OL,9,FGroup Newspapers paid a settlement and
OL,10,Fexpressed regret for the distress
OL,11,Fcaused.
OL,13,F"We weren't celebrities. This wasn't
OL,14,Fsalacious gossip. We were just normal
OL,15,Fpeople who got involved in a horrific
OL,16,Fincident. When something like this
OL,17,Fhappens, it makes you feel very
OL,18,Fvulnerable and that's very, very hard
OL,19,F."
