OL,4,C'vindicated' Prince Harry on impact of
OL,5,Chacking
OL,7,F"In 2011 an apology was published by
OL,8,FNGN to victims of voicemail
OL,9,Finterception by the News of the World.
OL,10,FThe company publicly committed to
OL,11,Fpaying financial compensation and
OL,12,Fsince then has paid settlements to
OL,13,Fthose with proper claims.
OL,15,F"In some disputed cases, it has made
OL,16,Fcommercial sense to come to a
OL,17,Fsettlement agreement before trial to
OL,18,Fbring a resolution to the matter. As
OL,19,Fwe reach the tail end of the
OL,20,Flitigation NGN is drawing a line under
OL,21,Fthe disputed matters.
